parts-87c7-45fa-acf9-f04aa4729872398.name: BEENLEIGH SPROCKET
parts-87c7-45fa-acf9-f04aa4729872398.description: Celebrate 40 years of Beenleigh BMX Park with this special release, limited edition BMX sprocket. Launched as part of the Transitions Book by Unscene History documenting the 40 year history of Doug Larsen Park, home of the infamous Beenleigh BMX Park. Subtle mentions of key groups, ramps, sayings & more with a black on black style. Retro inspired Colony Beeneligh 40 years CD style BMX sprocket, keeping the design clean with a single locator bolt.
